title: Bring your family home! Home in Seattle. 2 Beds, 1 Baths
posting_body: ['Delightful corner lot Highland Park bungalow!', 'Bathe in natural light from this bright and cheery 2 bedroom home with gleaming hardwoods, new carpet, a freshly painted interior, large picture windows, tiled full bath, new light fixtures and more.', 'Enjoy the large kitchen that features maple cabinets, granite counters, a new electric range and new dishwasher that sits conveniently adjacent to the laundry/mudroom with built in cabinets and exterior access.', "Level and private partially fenced yard with new parking pad, storage shed, garden space and a new front deck that's perfect for kicking back and relaxing on hot summer days.", 'Excellent West Seattle location for commuters, plus near shopping, parks, restaurants and more.', 'Welcome home!', '***Please Text & Call', 'show contact info', 'For More Details & Pics***']
